      <title>由于银行家的涌入，华尔街的奖金略有下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/wall-street-bonuses-decline-slightly-amid-an-influx-of-bankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年华尔街的平均奖金略有下降，原因是银行在交易持续低迷的情况下控制了薪酬，而证券行业的员工人数有所增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/wall-street-bonuses-decline-slightly-amid-an-influx-of-bankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
